ctions, scraped-back passages and reworked skies left visible rather than tidied away. There’s a steady rhythm between quick notations and slower, more structured compositions.</p><p>A highlight lands with the move from open coast to sheltered corners, hotel terraces, courtyards and gardens, where pattern and architecture take over from panorama. Henri Matisse’s Nice years act as a touchstone for interiors that trap southern light on tiled floors and pale walls. Pierre Bonnard at Le Cannet shifts the heat into domestic space, pushing colour until a room seems to glow from within. A thread on Pablo Picasso around Vallauris adds bite, with forms pared down until the scene reads in blocks of sun and shade.</p><p>Two don’t-miss elements come through clearly. First, a room of harbour and promenade images, masts, parasols, striped awnings and fast shadows, where brushwork stays brisk and decisions feel immediate. Second, the section on colour economy, where limited palettes still hold midday intensity, and labels call out the work of choosing a handful of pigments that don’t turn to mud under strong light.</p><p>The hidden gem sits slightly off the main flow, a quieter pocket of works on paper. Pencil scaffolding, wash tests, small compositional grids and margin notes give away the planning under a breezy shoreline view, and the paper itself carries the story, buckled edges, rubbed highlights, and thumbprints caught in dried pigment.</p><p>A few grounded studio bits sit nearby, paint boxes, palette knives and dog-eared sketchbooks, plus small maps and photographs that pin specific bays and towns to the images on the walls.</p>\n", 'max_output_tokens': 9000, 'model': 'gpt-5.2', 'reasoning': {'effort': 'medium'}, 'text': {'verbosity': 'low', 'format': {'type': 'json_schema', 'name': 'temp_translation_bundle', 'strict': True, 'schema': {'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False, 'properties': {'fr': {'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False, 'properties': {'name': {'type': 'string'}, 'short': {'type': 'string'}, 'long': {'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['name', 'short', 'long']}, 'es': {'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False, 'properties': {'name': {'type': 'string'}, 'short': {'type': 'string'}, 'long': {'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['name', 'short', 'long']}, 'it': {'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False, 'properties': {'name': {'type': 'string'}, 'short': {'type': 'string'}, 'long': {'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['name', 'short', 'long']}, 'ru': {'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False, 'properties': {'name': {'type': 'string'}, 'short': {'type': 'string'}, 'long': {'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['name', 'short', 'long']}, 'zh-CN': {'type': 'object', 'additionalProperties': False, 'properties': {'name': {'type': 'string'}, 'short': {'type': 'string'}, 'long': {'type': 'string'}}, 'required': ['name', 'short', 'long']}}, 'required': ['fr', 'es', 'it', 'ru', 'zh-CN']}}}}}
